OL,3,CParents who bought gun for teenage
OL,4,Cschool shooter sentenced
OL,6,FThe parents of a Michigan teenager who
OL,7,Fshot dead four fellow students with a
OL,8,Fgun bought by the couple have each
OL,9,Fbeen sentence to 10-15 years in prison.
OL,11,FJurors found guilty on four counts of
OL,12,Finvoluntary manslaughter after they
OL,13,Fignored their 15-year-old son's mental
OL,14,Fhealth needs, and bought him a gun
OL,15,Fthat he used days later in the school
OL,16,Fshooting.
