OL,3,CParents who bought gun for teenage
OL,4,Cschool shooter sentenced
OL,6,FEthan Crumbley killed students Tate
OL,7,FMyre, 16; Hana St Juliana,14; Madisyn
OL,8,FBaldwin, 17, and Justin Shilling, 17,
OL,9,Fwith a semi-automatic handgun at
OL,10,FOxford High School in 2021.
OL,12,FHe is now serving life in prison
OL,13,Fwithout parole.
OL,15,FThe families of the young victims gave
OL,16,Fvictim impact statements ahead of
OL,17,Ftheir sentencing.
