OL,4,Cschool shooter sentenced
OL,6,FJustin Shilling's father said "the
OL,7,Fblood of our children is on your hands
OL,8,Ftoo", while his mother said: "It
OL,9,Fdoesn't appear either of you even
OL,10,Fwanted or cherished your son, but I
OL,11,Fwanted and cherished mine".
OL,13,FThis is the first time the parents of
OL,14,Fa child who carried out a mass
OL,15,Fshooting have been held liable.
OL,17,FOn the day of the shooting, the
OL,18,FCrumbleys cut short a school meeting
OL,19,Fabout a disturbing drawing their son
OL,20,Fhad made, leaving him at the school.
