OL,3,CParents who bought gun for teenage
OL,4,Cschool shooter sentenced
OL,6,FSchool staff later sent him back to
OL,7,Fclass without checking his backpack,
OL,8,Fwhich contained the murder weapon.
OL,10,FPolice charged the Crumbleys within
OL,11,Fdays of the shooting, but were forced
OL,12,Fto launch a manhunt after they failed
OL,13,Fto appear for a hearing.
OL,15,FJennifer Crumbley stated that her
OL,16,Fstatement in the trial that "she would
OL,17,Fnot do anything differently" was
OL,18,Fmisunderstood, and insisted that she
OL,19,Fand her husband "were good parents".
