OL,4,Cschool shooter sentenced
OL,6,FJames Crumbley said in an emotional
OL,7,Fstatement to the families present: "I
OL,8,Fhave cried for you and the loss of
OL,9,Fyour children more than I can count".
OL,11,FDefence lawyers have argued that the
OL,12,FCrumbleys were responsible for "one
OL,13,Fgrossly negligent act" rather than
OL,14,Ffour separate criminal acts.
OL,16,FThe judge agreed with prosecutors that
OL,17,Fthis would be akin to acting as if
OL,18,Fonly one child was shot dead.
